cast.original_title: Going Clear: Scientology and the Prison of Belief
cast.overview: GOING CLEAR intimately profiles eight former members of the Church of Scientology, shining a light on how they attract true believers and the things they do in the name of religion.
cast.title: Going Clear: Scientology and the Prison of Belief

details.biography: Marjorie Cameron Parsons Kimmel (1922-1995) was an artist, occultist, actress, and wife of rocket pioneer and occultist Jack Parsons. Cameron played a major role in the 1946 Babalon Working ritual.
details.name: Marjorie Cameron
